Switch If several measurements are opened with this slider you can select which measurement results to display and use for the PDF document. Selection Clicking this button will close the measurement near the name of which it is located. If it is not saved it will be asked to save it. Close This button appears when the photometer is connected, provided that the device has OTG technology support. When you click on it, you can load the measurement results from the device. Download The Photometer program is designed to work with the photometer "PF-14 Agrovector", the results of the measurements of this laboratory and related files, to generate reports on measurements. The following describes how the program works. Help Here you can enter or change information about the field and a note to it. Information Click this button to open existing measurement files, files with information about the field or with a note to them. Open OTG technology is not supported on your device. This means that the photometer "Agrovector PF-14", when connected via USB, to the device will not be seen. All other features of the program: viewing and editing of already created measurement files, field information and notes, creating a report based on the data entered - will work correctly. OTG not supported Here you can view the document generated from the entered data. Document Here you can customize the data about the company and the logo that are displayed when creating a PDF document. Setting up the document Pressing this button opens a menu for saving unsaved files. Save Use the bottom panel to navigate through the application. When you click on the "Watch" button, a tab opens with information about the open measurement files. Watch Do not show again. OTG support:
